  m_Text: "How To Play:\n\nCharge the Plunger to launch the ball, \nscore points
    by having your ball hit\nthe bumpers, and use the flippers \nto prolong how long
    your ball remains\non the table\n\n\nControls:\n\n- Hold SPACE to charge plunger\n-
    A & D to activate Flippers"
